<p>英 /plʌs/    美 /plʌs/  </p>
<p>[非正式用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>并且；而且：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mobile phones are small and useful. Plus they are cheaper than before.
手机小巧、实用，另外也比以前便宜了。</p><footer>北师大④ – 10</footer></div></div>